title: Show HN: ChatGPT but for Rap Battles
text:
I made a thing! I made something I thought was fun with the latest OpenAI GPT 3.5 model.

It lets you rap battle against famous figures (Abraham Lincoln, Kim Kardashian etc) or against a generic A.I. You can also generate rap lyrics about any topic.

I've set it to give away 180 words for free so you can try it out, you'll have to confirm your email for this.

Hope you have fun :)

Tell HN: I've been banned from Twitter for defending myself from defamation
text:
Been a Twitter member since 2007.

Crystal D. Pryor, who I was married to, falsely accused me of stealing $70,000 of my own money to other people.

She also committed many, many counts of perjury. The judge took her at her word, even when presented with proof beyond a reasonable doubt that she was committing perjury. So I started posting proof online, including my full bank account statements, which clearly show her stealing the money, not me.

I posted these to Twitter as well. They banned me.
